Phase 3 v2 added `pricing_rules.organisation_id` and 6 new rule_types. M7 admin panel will need a CRUD UI for these rows. After every UPDATE/INSERT, the admin handler MUST call `invalidatePricingRule({ ruleType, countryCode, currency, organisationId })` from `@/lib/payments/pricing-rules` so the change propagates within one read. Full contract documented in closure-report-v2.md §3.1.

